name: Samutkarsh Pratishthhan
briefDescription: Samutkarsh Pratishthhan established in 2009 and duly registered with charity commissioner under societies registration act. Samutkarsh working for the cause of Old age health , rights of senior citizens, right of disabled, chronically ill bed ridden patients to get accessibility to health services. Samutkarsh also determined to bring equity in health care services and to fill the gap between rural and urban health as well gender disparities in health care services.

address: ND42 D3 Holkar Nagar , Opp Vasantrao Naik college
